verses.text: \w It|strong="H3117"\w* \w is|strong="H3117"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* good thing \w to|strong="H3117"\w* give thanks \w unto|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w sing|strong="H7892"\w* \w praises|strong="H7892"\w* \w unto|strong="H3117"\w* \w thy|strong="H3117"\w* name, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* Most High:

\w To|strong="H3068"\w* shew \w forth|strong="H2167"\w* \w thy|strong="H3068"\w* lovingkindness \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* morning, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w thy|strong="H3068"\w* faithfulness \w every|strong="H3068"\w* night,

\w With|strong="H3915"\w* an instrument \w of|strong="H2617"\w* ten strings, \w and|strong="H1242"\w* \w with|strong="H3915"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* psaltery; \w with|strong="H3915"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* solemn sound upon \w the|strong="H5046"\w* harp.

\w For|strong="H5921"\w* thou, \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, hast made \w me|strong="H5921"\w* glad \w through|strong="H5921"\w* \w thy|strong="H5921"\w* work: \w I|strong="H5921"\w* will triumph \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w works|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w thy|strong="H5921"\w* hands.

\w How|strong="H3588"\w* great \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w thy|strong="H3068"\w* \w works|strong="H4639"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*! \w thy|strong="H3068"\w* thoughts \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w very|strong="H8055"\w* deep.
\w A|strong="H3068"\w* brutish man knoweth not; neither \w doth|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fool understand \w this|strong="H3068"\w*:

\w When|strong="H3045"\w* \w the|strong="H3045"\w* wicked spring as \w the|strong="H3045"\w* grass, \w and|strong="H3045"\w* \w when|strong="H3045"\w* \w all|strong="H3045"\w* \w the|strong="H3045"\w* workers \w of|strong="H3045"\w* iniquity do flourish; \w it|strong="H3045"\w* \w is|strong="H3684"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w* \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w shall|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* destroyed \w for|strong="H3045"\w* \w ever|strong="H3808"\w*:
\w But|strong="H7563"\w* \w thou|strong="H3644"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, art \w on|strong="H3605"\w* high \w for|strong="H5704"\w* \w evermore|strong="H5703"\w*.

\w For|strong="H3068"\w*, lo, thine enemies, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, \w for|strong="H3068"\w*, lo, thine enemies \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* perish; \w all|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* workers \w of|strong="H3068"\w* iniquity \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* scattered.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* horn hast \w thou|strong="H3588"\w* exalted \w like|strong="H3068"\w* \add the horn of \add*\w the|strong="H3605"\w* wild-ox: \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* anointed \w with|strong="H3068"\w* fresh oil.

\w Mine|strong="H7311"\w* eye also hath seen \add my desire \add*\w on|strong="H7161"\w* \w mine|strong="H7311"\w* enemies, \w mine|strong="H7311"\w* ears have heard \add my desire \add*\w of|strong="H7161"\w* \w the|strong="H7311"\w* evil-doers \w that|strong="H8081"\w* \w rise|strong="H7311"\w* \w up|strong="H7311"\w* against \w me|strong="H7311"\w*.

\w The|strong="H5921"\w* righteous \w shall|strong="H5869"\w* flourish \w like|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* palm tree: \w he|strong="H5921"\w* \w shall|strong="H5869"\w* grow \w like|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cedar \w in|strong="H5921"\w* Lebanon.

They \w that|strong="H6662"\w* \w are|strong="H6662"\w* planted \w in|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* house \w of|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H6662"\w* \w flourish|strong="H6524"\w* \w in|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* courts \w of|strong="H6662"\w* our God.

\w They|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* still \w bring|strong="H6524"\w* \w forth|strong="H6524"\w* fruit \w in|strong="H3068"\w* old age; \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* full \w of|strong="H1004"\w* sap \w and|strong="H3068"\w* green:

\w To|strong="H1961"\w* shew \w that|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* upright; he \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w my|strong="H1961"\w* rock, \w and|strong="H5750"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w no|strong="H1961"\w* unrighteousness \w in|strong="H5750"\w* \w him|strong="H1961"\w*.
